    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken meticulous care of every single detail, and it drives like an absolute dream. You really have to see it in person to appreciate how flawless it is. If you're looking for that brand-new feel without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
