    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that remains in showroom condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in an exterior finish that is entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections. The paint retains its original deep luster, complemented by pristine alloy wheels and factory-spec tires. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and the carpets are flawless. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision, and the interior still carries that distinctive new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history that documents its pampered life. This is a rare opportunity to own the finest surviving example of this model, perfect for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
