      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six exhibits razor-sharp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies, with the dual-VANOS system operating flawlessly across the entire power band. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, the drivetrain delivers linear power with mechanical transparency. The chassis remains exceptionally rigid, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a fully refreshed suspension utilizing OEM bushings and Bilstein dampers. Finished in pristine Alpine White over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. This is a turn-key, collector-grade specimen with comprehensive service records including rod bearing replacement and valve adjustments.",
